===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|wherfor}}, {{m|enm|wherfore}}, {{m|enm|hwarfore}}, equivalent to {{compound|en|where|t1==what|for}}. Compare {{cog|nl|waarvoor||what for, wherefore}}, {{cog|de|wofür||for what, what for, why}}, {{etyl|da|-}} and {{etyl|no|-}} {{m|da|hvorfor||wherefore, why}}, {{cog|sv|varför||wherefore, why}}. More at {{m|en|where}}, {{m|en|for}}.

